<template>
  <Calendar />
  <!-- <DatePicker v-model="date"> -->

<script>
import { Calendar, DatePicker } from 'v-calendar';

export default {
  components: {
    Calendar,
    DatePicker,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      date: new Date(),
    };
  },
}
</script>
